{"tid":1375382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"致所有擔心仔女安全而唔俾仔女出街既父母","createTime":"2019-07-28T05:00:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T05:10:39.000Z","uid":222652,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"694e57852e8f9a0b28ca728bd1310a14e7db8721","tid":1375382,"uid":222652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:00:01.000Z","msg":"你地話你係政治冷感，唔關心政治，剩係關心仔女既安全，咁我想請你地，如果真係擔心我地既安全，就陪我地一起上街。<br />\n<br />\n你話你要搵食，要養家，所以唔出黎遊行，但奇怪既係，你又唔俾仔女出黎。咁我想問你地，到底一日既人工重要啲，定你地既仔女安全重要啲?<br />\n<br />\n一個真係關心仔女既父母，係應該耐心同仔女溝通，了解佢地既諗法，更乎者要保護佢地既安全，唔好一味得個講字。<br />\n<br />\n如果你唔上街，請不要阻止我地上街。"},{"pid":"253a2ff4b6e872f18256c1e93d2b7bc4aeb7a7f6","tid":1375382,"uid":222652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:01:17.000Z","msg":"請你地唔好咁自私，真係企出黎"},{"pid":"ccd3393dd39e1a0ed370f981515f2839def18281","tid":1375382,"uid":222652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:01:35.000Z","msg":"香港社會係我地人人都有份"},{"pid":"5dfeca789bd0a5cdc741bbe18eca4951f77f8b7e","tid":1375382,"uid":222652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:02:18.000Z","msg":"請你地真係出黎保護我地"},{"pid":"406b9ab56d1674a4813aab0aa0ca74ef1fd94d5b","tid":1375382,"uid":222652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:04:18.000Z","msg":"真係燒到埋身啦😭😭"},{"pid":"cf6a2e4eef563f96f404fe371b11990117debe83","tid":1375382,"uid":222652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:06:26.000Z","msg":"出黎啦"},{"pid":"df19eca526552a0b7c2dfaef6de23a7388a49bbb","tid":1375382,"uid":222652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:06:42.000Z","msg":"就算唔為你地自己，為下我地依一代"},{"pid":"4ce9da2ccf41a6a955e507c35da19af38b857487","tid":1375382,"uid":222652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:07:09.000Z","msg":"就算唔為我地依一代，諗下你地啲孫會過成點"},{"pid":"4515f445a9a811caf37a9191cc6b5af58c3fa6ff","tid":1375382,"uid":222652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"